Package: nostR
Title: The nostr R NSA API Wrapper
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Kevin", "Bolger", , "kevin@kevinbolger.xyz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a wrapper interface for the NSA API
    (https://github.com/garyokeeffe/NSA), allowing users to easily access
    and analyze data from the NSA. It includes functions for authentication,
    data retrieval, and data manipulation.
